6.  DATA PRIVACY AND ETHICS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

The Work is derived from anonymized real user interactions. The Recipient
expressly acknowledges and agrees to:

(a) Treat all data with appropriate sensitivity and in compliance with
    applicable data protection regulations (including but not limited to
    GDPR, PIPL, and CCPA where applicable);

(b) Immediately notify the Licensor at mengze.hong@connect.polyu.hk upon
    inadvertent discovery of any potentially personally identifiable
    information within the Work;

(c) Not combine the Work with other datasets in a manner that enables
    re-identification of individuals;

(d) Comply with all applicable ethical review requirements at the
    Recipient's institution before using the Work.

